		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场力发生装置将在场地内持续产生不断长大的裂隙，石砂从其间迸出，造成<span color="#ffe599">80%</span><span>伤害，裂隙范围较实验性力场发生装置大。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="419" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场力发生装置产生振荡地面的晶岩浪朝，碰到造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，施放3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="437" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场力发生装置唤起4根残缺石柱，依次朝目标发射，造成<span color="#ffe599">80%,40%,8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
